Summary: white blinking orb w/ yellow triangle light projecting below
divs: sighting detailsi saw this object on the way to the community gym. i came back at 8:35 pm and the object was gone, but there were two jets (sounding like f-18 engine)flying in a circular pattern. i saw this same object on 10\17\13 around 7:30 pm when i was driving on n. landing st headed ssw on princess anne. the object was nw of my position. i continued to see it as i turned on nimmo hwy and all the way into my community (west neck\signature rd). the object was unusual in shape, very bright, and twinkling. i had no idea what the object was, but i knew that is was not a plane (did not move, no navigation lights), nor was it a helicopter (no sound), and was much larger than the background stars. i was frightened when i arrived home and continued to observe the object (about 15 minutes) on 10\17. i went inside my condo and had dinner.
